full_text: There’s three sides to every story. His side. Her side. And the truth. But it sure is interesting when the truth stares you right in the face. 🗣🗣🗣

I just walked into a head shop down the block from my normal head shop just to see the competition… found out they sell porn on DVD and crack pipes. Needless to say I’m never walking in there again. 😂😂😂😂

Well I guess that’s pretty cool. Sucks when you think you’re cool with someone but apparently they think you’re a snake even tho you did literally nothing to them. It’s all good tho, bunny. No hard feelings. Sorry you feel that way tho. 🤷🏾‍♂️ (run tell that, folks)
